Name: libpng
URL: https://github.com/pnggroup/libpng
Version: 1.6.58
Update Mechanism: Manual
CPEPrefix: cpe:/a:libpng:libpng:1.6.58
Security Critical: no
Shipped: no
License: Libpng-2.0, Libpng
License File: LICENSE
License Android Compatible: yes

Description:
- Copied sources from v<version> tag upstream.
- Dropped unused files.
- Use custom configuration file pnglibconf.h, which was at one point a
  deliberate selection of libpng features to enable in Chrome. The
  file hasn't been updated one way or another to reflect features added in
  newer library versions.
- Configures custom png chunk user limits (crbug.com/117369) in pnglibconf.h.
- Keeps the fuzz target in contrib/oss-fuzz/ for running on clusterfuzz.
